            ; — one forward (alpha) + one backward (beta) yields d loss/d logit for
            ; every logit at once (softmax minus alignment-posterior), replacing
            ; the O(params) numerical gradient with O(T*S). Proven four-way by
            ; EXACT agreement with finite differences (band 127). Two walker-caught
            ; fkwu-leniencies fixed on the way (a paren, an out-of-bounds nth) — the
